description:
Welcome to Calamity, a custom Minecraft map made by Moesh. Players gather resources in the world and through renewable resource pads. The goal is to reach the enemy's bastion and press the button to start their experimental machine. The game is played in adventure mode so proper tools are need to mine the blocks.

Map Download: http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1769657-151-pvpadv-daligulv-studios-presents-calamity-by-moesh/
